4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course where students can become web development experts and learn how to build applications from scratch. The course duration is 16+2 weeks, with 3 classes weekly. No previous coding skills or advanced math are required. Students have the option to choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The program includes learning popular programming languages like Python and JavaScript, algorithm scripting, building apps using front-end libraries, utilizing APIs, and developing a final project. At the end of the course, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. The course is taught by experienced instructors and offers the opportunity to gain hands-on experience. For more information, visit their website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer. stop